---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Brand &amp; Product Marketing &middot; Bay Area</p>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">
        My former manager<br />
        called me a <span class="campfire">campfire</span>.
      </h1>
      <div class="hero-body">
        <p>
          I think what he meant was that when things are stuck, I have a way of getting them moving.
        </p>
        <p>
          My background sits at the intersection of CPG brand management and tech product marketing.
          At P&amp;G I learned how to run a brand like a business: consumer research, P&amp;L
          ownership, agency management, full-funnel execution. At Adobe I learned to do the same in
          an environment driven by product data and funnel metrics.
        </p>
        <p>
          The combination means I can move between brand strategy, product marketing, and GTM,
          without needing to start from scratch each time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="/images/headshot.jpg" alt="Junior Hou" class="headshot" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 5rem var(--pad-x) 4rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .campfire {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: sticky;
    top: 5rem;
  }

  .headshot {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 58% center;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero-image {
      position: static;
      max-width: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>
